<p>News coming from the Russian front very discouraging.  Heavy bombardment going on out on the Ypres sector.</p>
<p>Saturday 8.9.17<br/>Number of N.C.Os &amp; men crimed for having overstayed their leave in "Blighty".<br/>Cpl Herford &amp; L/Cpl Hand both reduced to the ranks, few other crimed.  Walked to 2nd Div Cinema show at Arques</p>
<p>Sunday 9.9.17<br/>Took a run to St Omer for a few hours.  Met Roy McPhee &amp; spent some time in conversation about old times.</p>
<p>Monday 10.9.17<br/>Usual morning parade, spent evening with the transport boys.  Getting more sick of</p>
